cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.NE 

This paper is about deep Reinforcement Learning (RL) and its application to Atari games. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.CV (Computer Vision) since the algorithm uses deep neural networks to process visual input. The paper also addresses the challenges of long-term planning and efficient exploration, which are relevant to robotics (cs.RO) and neural networks (cs.NE) as well.
